              "type": "string",
              "value": "- Generate an immediate action `oraImmediateInsight`:\n  - `followUpCommand`: ora.Invoke(actionSwitchAppContext, {\"personId\":\"{{$context.$nodes.PARSE_PAYLOAD.$output.result.personId}}\"})\n\n- Generate the following message:\n  App will refresh with new Person context: PersonId - {{$context.$nodes.PARSE_PAYLOAD.$output.result.personId}}, and reload all sections.\n\n- Return both the immediate action and the message together.\n- Do not ask for clarification or include any extra commentary."
            },
